NatSQL: select singer.Name from singer where count ( song.* ) > 1 group by singer.Name
prev_natsql: select singer.Name from singer where count ( song.* ) > 1 group by singer.Name

question: [struct_sep0] Show the names of singers and the total sales of their songs . [/struct_sep0]
query: SELECT T1.Name ,  sum(T2.Sales) FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name
NatSQL: select singer.Name , sum ( song.Sales ) from singer group by singer.Name

question: [struct_sep0] What is the feature type name of feature AirCon ? [/struct_sep0]

question: [struct_sep0] What are the names of properties [/struct_sep0] [struct_sep1] that are either House or [/struct_sep1] [struct_sep2] Apartment with more than 1 room ? [/struct_sep2]
